"http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_mad.gif" align=absmiddle>  the cruelty of friendship</span><hr size=1> Are friends crusial for a person's life? If so...how come so many people are so unloyal? From my experience...my so called friends only used me to get to point A to Point B. I was involved in 2 car accident in a week and a half and I got injured pretty bad (I do not want your pitty). After those accident, they all abanded me. I never eared from them again. I called and they ignored. How can one put all this behind him and forget it all. How can you expect me to trust in people again? My heart is full of rage. I was once a gentle, happy-go-lucky boy and I was really helpful and always there for people who needed help. Now, an evil as awaken in me. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START >: --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/mad.gif ALT=">:"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I don not love to be this way and I was hoping that you could convince me other wise and destroy this evil inside me! Show me what friendship can do! If you cannot convince me other wise then I will live my life by my own for ever. I just want your opinion...thats all and no more.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=otakulad>OtakuLad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Canadian <img src=http://contest.polykarbon.com/badge1.gif></span><br> <font color=#336699>(6/29/03 6:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2429.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><i